thing.title: Tentacle Ball
thing.author: syvwlch
thing.description: Yet another experiment in TopMod.This time I really went overboard and I don't think there is a way to print this without adding supports. In fact, you probably need one of those machines that sinters a powder layer by layer... like the CandyFab.Still, I liked how it looked so I thought I'd share. If this doesn't meet rule number one (a real, physical object that can be made), I'll take it down.
